item.title: About Me
item.description: This theme is created based on hugo-coder. I made it possible to tell yourself more by my change. Please see “FeaturesOfCoderPortfolio” in the post about the change. Regarding other demo contents, it is hugo-coder’s thing. Have questions or suggestions? Feel free to open an issue on GitHub or ask me on Twitter. Hugo is a static site engine written in Go.
